Zambujeira de Baixo Farm

Aljezur, Faro

Small farm located in Zambujeira de Baixo, parish of Odeceixe.
With an area of ​​16500 m2 and a ruin to be restored with 115 m2.
Electricity is on the property, the property borders a river with running water all year round.

Ideal for those who enjoy contact with Nature.

elements.title: AGRICULTURAL FARM ALONG THE ATLANTIC (SW-Places)
elements.contents:
Buy

AGRICULTURAL FARM ALONG THE ATLANTIC

Aljezur, Faro

Excellent Agricultural Farm that offers privacy in a serene and natural environment. With a total area of 11.6 hectares, with a “Paleolithic dune”, the abundant variety of vegetation and pine trees stands out, providing a unique atmosphere with great sun exposure. The soil is fertile, having previously been used for the production of sweet potatoes, and is certified in organic production mode (Certis and BioSuisse). Located in a protected area of the Costa Vicentina Natural Park, this property offers stunning sea views. Situated near Vila do Rogil and just 8 km from Aljezur, it allows easy access to all local amenities. Additionally, it is conveniently 30 minutes from Lagos and approximately 90 minutes from Faro Airport. The simple houses, with a total of 155 m2, can be expanded to 200 m2, plus 100 m2 of storage. With electricity and water supply from the public network, it is located in the ABM (water from the Irrigation Canal), a well and a pond (with a spring).
Distance to the beach: 700 m
Distance to the Center: 1000 m
View to: Countryside and Sea.

  • 7 Bedrooms
  • 3 WCs
  • 1 Kitchens

€ 1 800 000

Beach Villa

Aljezur, Faro

Majestic villa, spread over 3 floors where on the ground floor there is an entrance and distribution hall, 1 garage, 1 bedroom, 1 bathroom and a small apartment with independent entrance, consisting of an open-space kitchen, 2 bedrooms and a bathroom. On floor -1 there is a storage room and on floor +1 there is 1 common room with balcony, 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and a kitchen, also with a balcony, both with fabulous views over the dunes and the beach.
The villa is located on a plot of 2315.00m2, with a well and water cistern, the land is fertile and borders the river to the North, it is located very close to the beautiful Bordeira beach, right in the heart of the Natural Park and 5 minutes away Praia do Amado ex-libris of surfing in Southwest Portugal.
Property with potential for the installation of Local Accommodation, or as a family holiday home.

elements.title: EXCELLENT PROPERTY (SW-Places)
elements.contents:
Buy

EXCELLENT PROPERTY

Aljezur, Faro

House on a 1632m2 plot, 5 minutes from Arrifana beach and the cliffs of Costa Vicentina. The house was recently rehabilitated and modernized with good quality equipment, including a solid wood kitchen, wooden floors, a centrally positioned wood burning stove which, together with a heat pump, is the source of heating for the underfloor heating and hot water. , the frames are of good quality with double glazing.
The interior layout of the house was adapted to current times and experiences, namely the creation of an open space in the social area, with large openings to the exterior courtyard, promoting free circulation and integration of the respective spaces into the living spaces. The rehabilitation of the attic gave rise to a very tasteful en-suite bedroom space with several corners that support ideas for a wide variety of uses.
The outdoor patio has a wide variety of fruit trees, a vegetable garden area, and its formal garden. There is also a swimming pool with a support area located in the most sheltered area of the patio facing south.
Mark your visit.

For Alfambras lovers

Aljezur, Faro

The property with 1500m2 of land is located in the natural park in Alfambras and offers spectacular views over the whole of Alfambras. The beaches of Canal, Vale Figueiras and the Canal Resort Hotel are just a few minutes away.
The house with 173m2, double glazing and fireplace has 3 bedrooms and 4 bathrooms, three of which are en suite. An outdoor kitchen made of stainless steel and a pool with a wooden deck complete the whole thing. Access is quick and easy via asphalted roads. Nevertheless, the property is in a quiet location.
